	<div class="container promo-text">
		<div class="inner clearfix">
			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Big changes in the infosec landscape: Time to take note and take action</h1>
<div class="excerpt">There are big changes happening to the infosec landscape:, says ESET's Michael Aguilar. It's therefore time to take note and take action.</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
                <div class="wls-author with-avatar">
                            <div class="wls-author-avatar">
                    <a href="https://www.welivesecurity.com/author/maguilar/" title="Michael Aguilar">
                        <img src="https://www.welivesecurity.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/ID-Picture-222x179.png" alt="Michael Aguilar">
                    </a>
                </div>
                        <div class="wls-author-name">
                <a href="https://www.welivesecurity.com/author/maguilar/" title="Michael Aguilar">
                    Michael Aguilar                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
            </div>
    <span class="meta">
		<span class="strong">
			<time datetime="2017-05-08 14:00:28">8 May 2017 - 02:00PM</time>
		</span>
			</span>
</div>
